                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10176" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0395</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">242 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“铁锈记忆”到“数字星辰”：协力液压的数字化转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Rust to Resilience: XieLi Hydraulics’ Digital Transformation in China’s Manufacturing Landscape</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李广，翟胜宝，吴腾飞，梅焕群</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合肥协力液压科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；智能制造；政策协同</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital transformation；Smart manufacturing；Policy synergy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021年，合肥协力液压科技有限公司因数字化短板痛失核心客户，一场信任危机敲响了传统制造的警钟。从老厂区的“铁锈记忆”到新基地的“数字星辰”，这家民族液压企业以破釜沉舟之势开启转型。董事长赵岗赴德考察汲取智能工厂灵感，深感传统制造与国际顶尖企业差距，遂下定决心押注全新数字化工厂。面对巨额资金缺口，协力液压向政府借力，获得了国家“补短板”项目和地方政府政策支持。在数字化建设阶段，协力液压通过引入先进的FMS智能化生产线和自建智能检测线，实现了生产流程的数字化和智能化。面对变革阻力，协力液压以敏捷组织打破部门壁垒，更以“经验数字化”激活老技工智慧。三年淬炼，企业营收破亿，次品率锐减，终成行业“数字灯塔”。案例揭示了传统制造企业通过技术升级、政策协同与组织文化重塑实现转型的路径，为中小企业数字化转型提供了实践参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2021, Hefei Xieli Hydraulic Technology Co., Ltd., a Chinese hydraulic equipment manufacturer, faced a pivotal crisis after losing a core client due to inadequate digital capabilities, exposing vulnerabilities in traditional manufacturing. Determined to transform its legacy &quot;rust-belt&quot; operations into a smart manufacturing benchmark, the company initiated an all-in digital overhaul. Chairman Zhao Gang&#39;s fact-finding visit to German smart factories revealed critical gaps between domestic practices and global standards, prompting strategic investments in a next-gen digital plant. Leveraging China’s &quot;Strengthening Weak Links&quot; national policy and regional incentives, Xieli addressed funding constraints while deploying advanced FMS production lines and proprietary AI-powered quality inspection systems. To dismantle organizational resistance, it implemented agile management frameworks and a &quot;tacit knowledge digitization&quot; program that systematically converted veteran technicians’ expertise into digital workflows. After three years of transformation, the company achieved breakthrough results: annual revenues exceeded RMB 100 million with defective rates slashed sharply, earning recognition as an industrial &quot;Digital Lighthouse&quot;. This case exemplifies how traditional manufacturers can orchestrate digital leaps through technology-policy-culture synergy – integrating cutting-edge automation, state-backed initiatives, and cultural adaptation to preserve institutional knowledge while modernizing operations. It offers SMEs a replicable blueprint for balancing technological ambition with operational pragmatism in Industry 4.0 transitions.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">运营管理，创新与创业管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；创新理论；风险控制；企业绩效</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
